{"tid":1614977,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張達明：執法部門不受法律制約，損害法治，無法補救","createTime":"2019-10-03T02:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T03:02:51.000Z","uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"25cfaf0678d0c828d92158eeaa95cdfd4a4bff91","tid":1614977,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:59:55.000Z","msg":"曾任監警會成員的港大法律學院首席講師張達明表示，警務處處長盧偉聰在荃灣開槍事發後，未有完成調查和未有足夠資料前，已高調將事件定調是合法合理，會令外界質疑警方日後的調查，只是鞏固合法合理的講法，而不會相信能公正處理。<br />\n<br />\n張達明接受本台節目《千禧年代》訪問，他對事件感到痛心和擔心，亦令人氣憤，<span style=\"color: red;\">又說香港法例只是賦予警察可以使用合理武力，而合理武力是有客觀標準，並不是警員可以憑主觀標準，決定使用致命武力</span>。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，優秀的警隊不是從不犯錯和不能質疑，但自6月以來，凡遇到任何質疑，警方高層只是反駁說無問題，從無承認有過錯，認為這樣的情況是推翻過往數十年來警隊進步的成績。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">張達明指出，執法部門不受法律制約，對法治的損害是無法補救。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483998-20191003.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483998-20191003.htm&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7AweZXAU%2BhIfMqCJmwSRnXM%3D&h=64a7ff2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483998-20191003.htm&h=2e8cc21f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483998-20191003.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b0b73d84fb8fd616c0be9997d15c4578bf9bd949","tid":1614977,"uid":284485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hk